---
title: Cheesy Louisiana Beef Quesadillas with Charred Corn Salsa & Yoghurt
description: It’s the classic quesadillas again except we’re spicing things up with our fan-favourite Louisiana spice to coat the rich beef mince. Make it a little cheesy and add a golden corn salsa to tie it all together.
